HEADWORD: Remainder-man
<hw>Re*main"der-man</hw> <pr>(- m⟦acr⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Remainder-men</plw> <pr>(-m⟦ecr⟧n)</pr>.</plu>
